<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أخرجه أبو داود <span class="c2">(١٠٣٨)</span> وابن ماجه <span class="c2">(١٢١٩)</span> والبيهقي <span class="c2">(٢/ ٣٣٧)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
